？識得去搵佢地幫手，咁基本上對佢地都有基本了解，知道佢地運作等等。真係好好奇心態係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc0ce130aca971a71898d679f7b271de1930fa6","tid":1790412,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:40:00.000Z","msg":"不如成立一個良心商會佢做主席？"},{"pid":"46eb4c5816d32e83e88902e36e01df65f8a6e40a","tid":1790412,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:51:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">終於看到現實中的英雄本色，但...眼濕濕了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！</span></strong></span></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CyDQNxO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCyDQNxO.jpg&h=e4e7186a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9cf620e7b7fcde9f1202442907134486c275558c","tid":1790412,"uid":144492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:55:14.000Z","msg":"屌佢真係好好人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返工睇到眼濕濕"},{"pid":"cd3cc60e655526115c6530bf81879ce78d0e0c19","tid":1790412,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279058737850f61c8136cc06f26c5793d22413ac","tid":1790412,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:57:48.000Z","msg":"良心老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2c380fa7fcf83b79756fc1e0deeee47f8325cd","tid":1790412,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:58:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Sorry先，我㩒錯落左旨皮！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1f4